Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.08,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我的花朵曾昂然綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:16.95,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我曾光芒閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.85,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}可是太陽漸漸隱於地平線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.85,edchs,,0,0,25,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}一切都消失在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.25,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}夢中只剩下謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:28.09,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}唯我獨醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:30.99,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an9\fad(150,200)}只剩內心的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:34.06,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an9\fad(150,200)}迷茫著走向黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:39.29,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我拋棄了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:44.49,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}只願他們歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:50.20,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我的一切  深愛過的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:53.19,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}都去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.55,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}給我些回應吧
Comment: 0,0:22:56.59,0:23:01.89,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur2\fad(150,200)}不知不覺  眼淚也流乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:10.35,edchs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur2\fad(150,200)}我深愛的世界  已經回不來了
